1532 enum CombatManeuverReturns
1533 {
1534  // TODO: RETURN_NO_ACTION_UNKNOWN is not part of ANY_OK or ANY_ERROR. It's also bad form and should be eliminated ASAP.
1535  RETURN_NO_ACTION_OK = 0x01, // No action taken during this combat maneuver, as intended (just wait, etc...)
1536  RETURN_NO_ACTION_UNKNOWN = 0x02, // No action taken during this combat maneuver, unknown reason
1537  RETURN_NO_ACTION_ERROR = 0x04, // No action taken due to error
1538  RETURN_NO_ACTION_INVALIDTARGET = 0x08, // No action taken - invalid target
1539  RETURN_FINISHED_FIRST_MOVES = 0x10, // Last action of first-combat-maneuver finished, continue onto next-combat-maneuver
1540  RETURN_CONTINUE = 0x20, // Continue first moves; normal return value for next-combat-maneuver
1541  RETURN_NO_ACTION_INSUFFICIENT_POWER = 0x40, // No action taken due to insufficient power (rage, focus, mana, runes)
1542  RETURN_ANY_OK = 0x31, // All the OK values bitwise OR'ed
1543  RETURN_ANY_ACTION = 0x30, // All returns that result in action (which should also be 'OK')
1544  RETURN_ANY_ERROR = 0x4C // All the ERROR values bitwise OR'ed
1545 };

1583  // masters orders that should be obeyed by the AI during the updateAI routine
1584  // the master will auto set the target of the bot
1585  enum CombatOrderType
1586  {
1587  ORDERS_NONE = 0x0000, // no special orders given
1588  ORDERS_TANK = 0x0001, // bind attackers by gaining threat
1589  ORDERS_ASSIST = 0x0002, // assist someone (dps type)
1590  ORDERS_HEAL = 0x0004, // concentrate on healing (no attacks, only self defense)
1591  ORDERS_NODISPEL = 0x0008, // Dont dispel anything
1592  ORDERS_PROTECT = 0x0010, // combinable state: check if protectee is attacked
1593  ORDERS_PASSIVE = 0x0020, // bots do nothing
1594  ORDERS_TEMP_WAIT_TANKAGGRO = 0x0040, // Wait on tank to build aggro - expect healing to continue, disable setting when tank loses focus
1595  ORDERS_TEMP_WAIT_OOC = 0x0080, // Wait but only while OOC - wait only - combat will resume healing, dps, tanking, ...
1596  ORDERS_RESIST_FIRE = 0x0100, // resist fire
1597  ORDERS_RESIST_NATURE = 0x0200, // resist nature
1598  ORDERS_RESIST_FROST = 0x0400, // resist frost
1599  ORDERS_RESIST_SHADOW = 0x0800, // resist shadow
1600  ORDERS_MAIN_TANK = 0x1000, // main attackers binder by gaining threat in raid situation
1601  ORDERS_MAIN_HEAL = 0x2000, // concentrate on healing the main tank (will ignore other targets as long as MT needs healing)
1602  ORDERS_NOT_MAIN_HEAL = 0x4000, // concentrate on healing except the main tank that will be ignored
1603 
1604  // Cumulative orders
1605  ORDERS_PRIMARY = 0x7007,
1606  ORDERS_SECONDARY = 0x0F78,
1607  ORDERS_RESIST = 0x0F00,
1608  ORDERS_TEMP = 0x00C0, // All orders NOT to be saved, turned off by bots (or logoff, reset, ...)
1609  ORDERS_RESET = 0xFFFF
1610  };
